<body>

<header>
  <h1><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Your trust is our priority – ShaktiRide ensures your data stays safe and private.</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <section>
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to ShaktiRide. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information while you use our career guidance and personality development services.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect your name, email address, personality test results, career preferences, and interaction history with our platform.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>Your data helps us provide personalized career suggestions, improve our AI recommendations, and enhance your learning experience.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Data Protection & Security</h2>
    <p>We use encryption, secure servers, and access controls to ensure your personal information remains confidential and safe.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to request a copy of your data, ask for corrections, or delete your account anytime by contacting us.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Cookies Policy</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to improve your experience and provide relevant recommendations. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@ShaktiRide.com">privacy@ShaktiRide.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</div>

